items.title: At Least 10 Are Killed at Ski Resort Fire in Turkey
items.description: The fire at the Grand Kartal Hotel, in a ski resort in Bolu Province, started when most of the guests were asleep. The cause of the fire was unclear.

items.title: Fire at Turkey Ski Resort Kills at Least 10
items.description: The blaze broke out overnight at a popular ski resort during a school break when many families head to the slopes.
